      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kaß es tew tchoddeen pawehu to KUNGSII tawn Dee-wu mihtoht/ winna Zelfos stai-gaht/ un winna Baufius/ Lik-kunus un Teefas turreht/ ka tu dsihwo un wairojees / un tas KUNGS taws Deews tew swehti tai Semmê/ us kurren tu eij winnu eemantoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja tawa Sirdeß at-greesifees/ un ne klaufsifs/ un tu tapsi skubbinahts/ ka tu zittus Deewus peeluhgti/ un teem kal-post.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad pafluuddinaju es jums schodeen/ ka juhs wiſſai bohjâ eeteet / juhs ne dsihwoseet ilgi wirs tahs Semmes/ us kurren tu taggad pahr to Jardanuetij/ ka tu turp nahz winnu eemantoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es nemmu par Leezibu pahr jums schodeen to Debbeſi un to Semmi/ es efimu jums to Dsihwibu un to Nahwi / to Swehtumm / un tohs Lahstus preekſchlizzis / tad nu iſwehle to Dsihwibu/ ka tu dsihwo/ tu un taws Dsimmums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mihſtodams to KUNGU tawu Deewu / klaufidams win-na Balksnei / un winnam pee-fehrdamees/ jo wiꞥſch irr tawa Dsihwiba un tawu Deenu Pa-garrinaſchana/ ka tu paleezi wirs tahs Semmes / ko tas KUNgs taweem Tehweem Abbrahamam; Ihsaikam un Jehkabam ſweh-rejs irr winneem doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "winsch ar teem pahr toJardanu ne ees: 1 / 2. Eepreezina tobß arri: 5. Eezett Josuji par Waddonu : 7. Pawehi ka ikgaddus: 9. Jeptita Gaddâ aflaschia pehz teem Leewenwu Swehtkeem to Bauſlibas.Grahmatu lasiht buhs: 10. Deews to Kauschu Atkahpschanu papreekſch finna : 16. Un ezett Josuji Mohsus Weeta: 23. Pawehi to Bauſlibas.Grahu matu Derribas Schtirstâ fargaht: 24.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad nogahje Mohsus/ un Brunnaja schohs Wahrdus us wiſſiu Israëlu /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fazzija us teem: Es efmu fchodeen ſints un divide-finitês Gaddus wezz/ es ne warrefschu wairs iſeet nedß ee-eet/ un tas KUNGS irr us man fazzijs terw ne buhs pahr to Jardanu eet\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS taws Deewtas ees pats tawâ Preeſchâ pahri/ tas isdeldehs ſchihs Tautatawâ Preeſchâ/ ka tu tahs eemanto / Josuûs tas ees tawPreeſchâ pahri / ittin ka taKUNGS irr runnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS darrihe winneem/ ittin ka wiꞥſch darrijirr Sionam/ un Ogam to Amoriteru Rehuineem/ un winna Semmei/ ko wiꞥſch irr isdeldejs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas KUNGS tawâ Preeſchâ tohs nodohs / taibuhs jums winneem darriht/ pehwiffahm Pawehlefchanahm/ ko ejunis efimu pawehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eestiprinajeetceß / un turajt drohſchn Prahtu/ ne bihsteeteeß/ un ne bailojeetees preekſchwinneem/ jo tas KUNGS tawDeewu irr tas/ kas ar tewim eetwinsch terw ne atſtahs/ nedß tenpainettihs.\n"
    }
  ],
